#

Classic New York Steak with Chimichurri Sauce

$25
650 kcal

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

BeefSteakChimichurriMain Course

Description

Juicy New York steak topped with a vibrant chimichurri sauce for a zesty finish.

Ingredients

  • New York Strip Steak: 2 (8 oz each)
  • Olive Oil: 1/4 cup
  • Fresh Parsley: 1 cup, chopped
  • Fresh Cilantro: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Red Wine Vinegar: 1/4 cup
  • Crushed Red Pepper Flakes: 1 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
